StatisticDescription:
The number of non-inversions of a permutation.

For a permutation of $\{1,\ldots,n\}$, this is given by $\operatorname{noninv}(\pi) = \binom{n}{2}-\operatorname{inv}(\pi)$.
StatisticTitle: The number of non-inversions of a permutation.
StatisticReferences:
[1]  Reiner, V., Saliola, F., Welker, V. Spectra of Symmetrized Shuffling Operators [[arXiv:1102.2460]]
